      "content": "thanks for that. so i've been hearing some parents in the PTA group saying that the school is basically pushing an agenda and that the \"critics\" side is just being closed-minded or \"anti-science.\" at the same time, some other parents are saying the school is trying to undermine parents' rights. from what you've seen, is there any merit to the idea that the critics are just being reactionary, or is there a legitimate educational or philosophical basis for their concerns?",
